-- Tick function that will be executed every logic tick function onTick() if(vv_en == nil) then vv_en = property.getBool("Velocity vector") spd_en = property.getBool("Speed") alt_en = property.getBool("Altitude")
end
value = input.getNumber(1) -- Read the first number from the script's composite input output.setNumber(1, value * 10) -- Write a number to the script's composite output pitch = input.getNumber(1)*360 roll = input.getNumber(2)*360 speed = input.getNumber(3)*3.6 alt = input.getNumber(4) h_dir = input.getNumber(5) v_dir = input.getNumber(6) output.setNumber(1,v_dir - pitch)
end
-- Draw function that will be executed when this script renders to a screen function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() -- Get the screen's width and height h = screen.getHeight() --screen.drawCircleF(w / 2, h / 2, 30) -- Draw a 30px radius circle in the center of the screen
p_upx = math.sin(roll*math.pi/180) p_upy = math.cos(roll*math.pi/180) p_90x = math.sin((roll+90)*math.pi/180) p_90y = math.cos((roll+90)*math.pi/180)
screen.setColor(0, 0, 0) -- Set draw color to green screen.drawRectF(0,0,w,h)
if(alt_en) then for i= math.floor(alt-5) , math.floor(alt+5) do screen.setColor(16,16,32) screen.drawText(w-20,h/2+(alt-i)*12,string.format("%.1f",i)) end end
screen.setColor(0, 255, 0) -- Set draw color to green screen.drawLine(w/2 - p_90x * h/2 , h/2 - p_90y * h/2 , w/2 + p_90x * h/2 , h/2 + p_90y * h/2)
pm30 = math.floor((pitch-30)/10)*10
for i= pm30 , pm30 + 60 , 10 do i = i % 360 if(i > 180) then i = i-360 elseif(i < -180) then i = i+360 end
vx = -p_upx * (i-pitch) * h/60 vy = -p_upy * (i-pitch) * h/60 hx = p_90x * h/5 hy = p_90y * h/5 if(i>90) then i = 180-i elseif(i<-90) then i = -180-i end if((i>0 and i<180) or (i<-180)) then screen.setColor(i*255/90, 255, 255) else screen.setColor(0, 255+i*128/90, 0) end screen.drawLine(w/2 + vx + hx,h/2 + vy + hy,w/2 + vx - hx,h/2 + vy - hy) screen.drawText(w/2 + vx + hx,h/2 + vy + hy,i) screen.setColor(255, 255, 255)
end
if(spd_en) then screen.drawText(0,h/2,string.format("%.1f",speed)) screen.drawText(0,h/2-6,"Km/h") end if(alt_en) then screen.drawText(w-20,h/2,string.format("%.1f",alt)) screen.drawText(w-20,h/2-6,string.format("Alt.")) end
if(vv_en) then hx = w/2+h_dir*h/60 hy = h/2-v_dir*h/60
screen.drawLine(hx-5 , hy , hx+5 , hy) screen.drawLine(hx , hy -5 , hx , hy +5) end
end

function onTick() tiltX = input.getNumber(1) tiltY = input.getNumber(2) speed = input.getNumber(3)
end
function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight() wm = w/2 hm = h/2
tiltXText = tiltX*400 tiltXText = math.floor(tiltXText+0.5)
tiltYText = tiltY*400 tiltYText = math.floor(tiltYText+0.5)
tiltX = tiltX * 550 --gibt die geschwindigkeit an mit der die linien hoch und runter beweget werden tiltX = math.floor(tiltX+0.5) --round value
tiltY = (tiltY * math.pi/2)/0.25 --rechnet tiltY in radialwinkel um
lineRate = -math.sin(math.abs(tiltY)) * 5 + 10 --gibt de abstand zwischen den linien an ... siehe line 27 lineRate = math.floor(lineRate+0.5)
screen.setColor(0, 255, 0, 50)
for i=1,h do --durchleauft alle y koordinaten if ((i-tiltX)%lineRate == 0) then --fragt wann line gezeichnet werden soll
shiftY = math.tan(tiltY)*(i-hm) --gibt an wie viel die linien nach links oder recht bewegt werden sollen
v1 = 5 * math.cos(tiltY) --siehe blatt if (tiltY>0) then v1 = v1 * (-1) --invertiere fuer neigung nach rechts end
v2 = math.sqrt(25-v1^2) --siehe blatt
x1 = ((wm)+shiftY) --ursprungspunkt der liene x x2 = i-2 --ursprungspunkt der liene y y1 = x1+v1 --endpunkt der liene siehe blatt y2 = x2+v2 --endpunkt der liene siehe blatt
screen.drawLine(x1, x2, y1, y2) --zeichne ein teil der linie y1 = x1-v1 --endpunkt auf der anderen seite des ursprungs y2 = x2-v2 screen.drawLine(x1, x2, y1, y2) end end
screen.setColor(255, 0, 0)
shiftY = math.tan(tiltY)*(tiltX+2) v1 = 10 * math.cos(tiltY) if (tiltY>0) then v1 = v1 * (-1) end v2 = math.sqrt(100-v1^2)
x1 = (wm)+shiftY x2 = hm+tiltX y1 = x1+v1 y2 = x2+v2 screen.drawLine(x1, x2, y1, y2) y1 = x1-v1 y2 = x2-v2 screen.drawLine(x1, x2, y1, y2)
--Draw plane screen.setColor(0, 255, 0) screen.drawLine(wm-5, hm+1, wm+6, hm+1) screen.drawLine(wm-5, hm, wm-20, hm) screen.drawLine(wm+5, hm, wm+10, hm) screen.drawRect(wm-1, hm-1, 2, 2)
drawText()
end
function drawText()
screen.setColor(0, 255, 0) if (tiltXText > -10 and tiltXText < 10) then if (tiltXText >= 0) then screen.drawText(w-11, hm-2, tiltXText) screen.drawRect(w-13, hm-4, 7, 8) else screen.drawText(w-16, hm-2, tiltXText) screen.drawRect(w-18, hm-4, 12, 8) end else if (tiltXText >= 0) then screen.drawText(w-11, hm-2, tiltXText) screen.drawRect(w-13, hm-4, 12, 8) else screen.drawText(w-16, hm-2, tiltXText) screen.drawRect(w-18, hm-4, 17, 8) end end
if (tiltYText < 0) then screen.drawTriangleF(wm-7, h-8, wm-7, h, wm-15, h-4) end if (tiltYText > 0) then screen.drawTriangleF(wm+8, h-8, wm+8, h, wm+16, h-4) end
tiltYText = math.abs(tiltYText) if (tiltYText < 10) then screen.drawText(wm-1, h-7, tiltYText) screen.drawRect(wm-3, h-9, 7, 8) else screen.drawText(wm-4, h-7, tiltYText) screen.drawRect(wm-6, h-9, 12, 8) end
speed = math.floor(speed+0.5)
if (speed < 10 and speed >= 0)then screen.drawText(wm-25, hm-2, speed) screen.drawRect(wm-27, hm-3, 7, 6) elseif ((speed < 100 and speed >=10) or (speed<0 and speed > -10)) then screen.drawText(wm-30, hm-2, speed) screen.drawRect(wm-32, hm-3, 12, 6) elseif ((speed < 1000 and speed >=100) or (speed<= -10 and speed > -100)) then screen.drawText(wm-35, hm-2, speed) screen.drawRect(wm-37, hm-3, 17, 6) elseif (speed >= 1000 or (speed<= -100 and speed > -1000)) then screen.drawText(wm-40, hm-2, speed) screen.drawRect(wm-42, hm-3, 22, 6)
end
end

mode = 1 off = false firstPush = false function onTick() -- Read the touchscreen data from the script's composite input inputX = input.getNumber(3) inputY = input.getNumber(4) isPressed = input.getBool(1)
modeUp = input.getBool(6) modeDown = input.getBool(5)
-- Check if the player is pressing the rectangle at (10, 10) with width and height of 20px AFDrequest = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 0, 0, 18, 9) MAPrequest = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 0, 10, 18, 9) SYSrequest = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 0, 20, 18, 9) OFFrequest = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 19, 0, 11, 29)
if (AFDrequest or ONrequest) then mode = 1 off = false elseif (MAPrequest) then mode = 2 elseif (SYSrequest) then mode = 3 elseif (OFFrequest) then mode = 0 end
if (modeUp and not firstPush) then if (mode > 2) then mode = 1 else mode = mode + 1 end firstPush = true elseif (modeDown and not firstPush) then if (mode < 2) then mode = 3 else mode = mode - 1 end firstPush = true end
if (not modeDown and not modeUp) then firstPush = false end
if (mode == 1) then output.setBool(1, false) output.setBool(2, false) elseif (mode == 2) then output.setBool(1, true) output.setBool(2, false) elseif (mode == 3) then output.setBool(1, false) output.setBool(2, true) elseif (mode == 0) then output.setBool(1, true) output.setBool(2, true) off = true end
end
function onDraw()
w = screen.getWidth() -- Get the screen's width and height h = screen.getHeight()
screen.setColor(0, 255, 0)
if (mode == 1) then screen.drawRect(1, 11, 17, 8) screen.drawText(3, 13, "MAP")
screen.drawRect(1, 21, 17, 8) screen.drawText(3, 23, "SYS")
screen.drawRect(20, 1, 10, 28) screen.drawText(23, 3, "O") screen.drawText(23, 13, "F") screen.drawText(23, 23, "F")
screen.drawRectF(1, 1, 18, 9) screen.setColor(0, 0, 0) screen.drawText(3, 3, "AFD") elseif (mode == 2) then screen.drawRect(1, 1, 17, 8) screen.drawText(3, 3, "AFD")
screen.drawRect(1, 21, 17, 8) screen.drawText(3, 23, "SYS")
screen.drawRect(20, 1, 10, 28) screen.drawText(23, 3, "O") screen.drawText(23, 13, "F") screen.drawText(23, 23, "F")
screen.drawRectF(1, 11, 18, 9) screen.setColor(0, 0, 0) screen.drawText(3, 13, "MAP") elseif (mode == 3) then screen.drawRect(1, 1, 17, 8) screen.drawText(3, 3, "AFD")
screen.drawRect(1, 11, 17, 8) screen.drawText(3, 13, "MAP")
screen.drawRect(20, 1, 10, 28) screen.drawText(23, 3, "O") screen.drawText(23, 13, "F") screen.drawText(23, 23, "F")
screen.drawRectF(1, 21, 18, 9) screen.setColor(0, 0, 0) screen.drawText(3, 23, "SYS") else screen.drawRect(1, 1, 17, 8) screen.drawText(3, 3, "AFD")
screen.drawRect(1, 11, 17, 8) screen.drawText(3, 13, "MAP")
screen.drawRect(1, 21, 17, 8) screen.drawText(3, 23, "SYS")
screen.drawRectF(20, 1, 11, 29) screen.setColor(0, 0, 0) screen.drawText(23, 3, "O") screen.drawText(23, 13, "F") screen.drawText(23, 23, "F") end
end
-- Returns true if the point (x, y) is inside the rectangle at (rectX, rectY) with width rectW and height rectH function isPointInRectangle(x, y, rectX, rectY, rectW, rectH) return x > rectX and y > rectY and x < rectX+rectW and y < rectY+rectH end

zoom = 25 customeMode = false GPSXcustome = 0 GPSYcustome = 0
function onTick() GPSX = input.getNumber(5) GPSY = input.getNumber(6)
inputX = input.getNumber(3) inputY = input.getNumber(4) isPressed = input.getBool(1)
zoomIN = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, w-9, h-18, 8, 8) zoomOUT = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, w-9, h-9, 8, 8)
up = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 9, h-27, 8, 8)--oben down = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 9, h-9, 8, 8)--unten left = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 0, h-18, 8, 8)--links right = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 18, h-18, 8, 8)--rechts reset = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 9, h-18, 8, 8)--mitte
if (zoomIN and zoom>0) then zoom = zoom - math.sin((zoom * math.pi/2)/50) * 0.5 elseif (zoomOUT and zoom<50) then zoom = zoom + math.sin((zoom * math.pi/2)/50) * 0.5 end
if (up and not customeMode) then GPSXcustome = GPSX GPSYcustome = GPSY + zoom customeMode = true elseif (up and customeMode) then GPSYcustome = GPSYcustome + zoom * 5 end
if (down and not customeMode) then GPSXcustome = GPSX GPSYcustome = GPSY - zoom customeMode = true elseif (down and customeMode) then GPSYcustome = GPSYcustome - zoom * 5 end
if (left and not customeMode) then GPSXcustome = GPSX - zoom GPSYcustome = GPSY customeMode = true elseif (left and customeMode) then GPSXcustome = GPSXcustome - zoom * 5 end
if (right and not customeMode) then GPSXcustome = GPSX + zoom GPSYcustome = GPSY customeMode = true elseif (right and customeMode) then GPSXcustome = GPSXcustome + zoom * 5 end
if (reset) then customeMode = false GPSXcustome = GPSX GPSYcustome = GPSY end
end
-- Draw function that will be executed when this script renders to a screen function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() -- Get the screen's width and height h = screen.getHeight() screen.setColor(255, 0, 0)
screen.setMapColorOcean(0, 0, 0, 0) screen.setMapColorShallows(0, 255, 0, 75) screen.setMapColorLand(0, 255, 0, 255) screen.setMapColorGrass(0, 255, 0, 255) screen.setMapColorSand(0, 255, 0, 255) screen.setMapColorSnow(0, 255, 0, 255)
if (not customeMode) then screen.drawMap(GPSX, GPSY, zoom) screen.drawRect(w/2, h/2, 1, 1) else screen.drawMap(GPSXcustome, GPSYcustome, zoom) end
screen.setColor(255, 0, 0) screen.drawRect(w-8, h-8, 6, 6) --minus screen.drawLine(w-6, h-5, w-3, h-5)
screen.drawRect(w-8, h-17, 6, 6) --plus screen.drawLine(w-5, h-13, w-5, h-16) screen.drawLine(w-6, h-14, w-3, h-14)
screen.drawRect(1, h-17, 6, 6) --links screen.drawLine(1, h-14, 7, h-14)
screen.drawRect(19, h-17, 6, 6) --rechts screen.drawLine(19, h-14, 25, h-14)
screen.drawRect(10, h-8, 6, 6) --unten screen.drawLine(13, h-8, 13, h-2)
screen.drawRect(10, h-26, 6, 6) --oben screen.drawLine(13, h-26, 13, h-20)
screen.drawRect(10, h-17, 6, 6) --mitte
end
-- Returns true if the point (x, y) is inside the rectangle at (rectX, rectY) with width rectW and height rectH function isPointInRectangle(x, y, rectX, rectY, rectW, rectH) return x > rectX and y > rectY and x < rectX+rectW and y < rectY+rectH end
